short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add KeepTradeCut player values to the Sleeper website.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
KeepTradeCut player values are added to the following sections of Sleeper:
-Player popups
-Matchup tab and popups
-Team tab
-Trend tab
-Trades tab and popups
-League Chat

Individual sections can be enabled/disabled in the extension options.

The extension makes a call to the Sleeper API with the league's id to check if it's dynasty or superflex, which is used to determine which KeepTradeCut values should show.


Version 1.1 changes:
-Fixed issue with values not displaying
-Cache KTC player values in browser session storage
